aVIt grows. It adds with sophistication.
p244
aVThis silkworm cocoon, for example,
p245
aVcreates a highly sophisticated architecture,
p246
aVa home inside which to metamorphisize.
p247
aVNo additive manufacturing today gets even close to this level of sophistication.
